    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_outside-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん\n突然呼び出してなんの用ですか？",
      "startTime": 2.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "「暇だ」って突然送ってきたのは怜の方じゃないか\nどうしたんだ？　旅行で暇だなんて聞いたことないぞ",
      "startTime": 10.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません。そういえばさっき送ったんでした\n旅行って何をしたらいいか分からなくて、つい",
      "startTime": 19.4851246516,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうなのか？　美味しいご飯を食べたり、普段は\n見られない景色を見たり……いくらでもあるだろう？",
      "startTime": 27.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "私も調べたんですけどいまいち楽しみ方が分からなくて\n家族旅行にもあまり行く機会がなかったですし……",
      "startTime": 37.8645351727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（……そうか、怜は少し前まで家族の仲が……俺は）\n（マネージャー失格だ。早く気付いてあげるべきだった）",
      "startTime": 47.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。暇なら、少し俺に任せてくれないか？\n怜に旅行の楽しさを教えてみせるよ",
      "startTime": 56.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "え、突然どうしたんですか……？\nなんか妙に意気込んでますけど……",
      "startTime": 64.2153284073,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "いや、せっかくの慰安旅行だ。怜にいい思い出を残して\nほしくてな。暇だからいいよな？",
      "startTime": 71.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "……さっきから暇、暇って……暇人扱いされるのは\nなんか嫌です！　暇だから行きますけど！",
      "startTime": 80.3932877541,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり北海道といえば食べ歩きだろう\n海の幸から珍味まで沢山あるぞ",
      "startTime": 90.366195794,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-snow-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 86.0266210874
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、お店だけじゃなくて屋台も一杯出ていますね\nお祭りみたいで賑やかです",
      "startTime": 99.0778683345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、ホタテに牡蠣、海鮮丼……あ、アイスもあるぞ\nどうだ？　一つと言わず、二つ、三つでもいいからな",
      "startTime": 106.1333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや……そんなに食べられませんよ\n私を太らせたいんですか？",
      "startTime": 114.4529707592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういう訳じゃないが、食べ歩きに遠慮は厳禁だからな\n食べたい物があったらすぐに言うんだぞ？",
      "startTime": 121.9666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい……なんか、今日は圧が凄いですね\n遠慮はしてないので大丈夫です",
      "startTime": 131.207598591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あの『蟹掴み取り』って書いてる屋台、人だかりが\n凄いですね。少し見てもいいですか？",
      "startTime": 140.107598591,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ……本当に生きてる蟹を掴むんですね。あの大きな\nハサミに挟まれたらと思うと……ちょっと怖いです",
      "startTime": 151.0742723784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "甲羅を掴めば挟まれることはないと思うぞ\nせっかくだし挑戦してみるか？",
      "startTime": 160.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも……やっぱりやめておきます\n目立ちそうだし、怖いし……",
      "startTime": 167.6071751278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "怜も気になってるんだろう？　旅行では普段やらない\nことも思い切って挑戦するのが思い出を作るコツだぞ",
      "startTime": 174.4333435059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "思い出を……わ、分かりました\nそこまで言うならやってみます……！",
      "startTime": 185.6221859616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、蟹の背中……ここを掴めばいいんですよね？\nいきますよ……えいっ！　け、結構重い……！",
      "startTime": 195.1221859616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "わ、ちょっと、暴れないで！　あっ……\n落としてしまいました。掴み取り失敗です……",
      "startTime": 205.588839404,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3126.350052999982,
          "startTime": 203.9555060706
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-pacha-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3126.350052999982,
          "startTime": 203.9555060706
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、でもまさか怜が一番大物の蟹を狙うとは\n思わなかったよ。随分思い切ったな",
      "startTime": 216.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei015.m4a",
      "text": "だって、せっかくなら大きい方がいいかなと思って……\n結局、失敗しちゃいましたけど……はぁ",
      "startTime": 227.2435785613,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに落ち込まないでくれ。怜の思い出作りだし\n俺も蟹掴み取りに挑戦するよ",
      "startTime": 236.7999969483,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_52_02-rei016.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんもやるんですか？\n気を付けて下さいね、結構暴れますから",
      "startTime": 242.2930116655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
